   "credential": 177,
   "scanner": 4
  },
  "updated": "2026-07-23T12:00:01Z",
  "update_frequency": "hourly",
  "license": "CC0-1.0",
  "field_notes": "tier: 'credential' or 'scanner'. For credential-tier entries, attempts = lifetime credential attempts and bans = ban cycles; for scanner-tier entries, attempts = connection events inside the current window and bans is always 0 \u2014 both tiers are firewalled on the sensor, but scanner ban cycles are tracked separately and are not counted in this field. first_seen and last_seen both describe observed attack activity inside the current window, so first_seen <= last_seen always holds. first_banned is bookkeeping \u2014 when this IP was first firewalled \u2014 and may fall outside the window or after last_seen; it is null for scanner-tier entries.",
  "disclaimer": "Provided as-is, no warranty. Entries may involve dynamic or reassigned IPs; verify before acting. Contact the maintainer for delisting.",
